<li id="cite_note-Mair-5">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Mair_5-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Mair_5-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFMair1990">Mair, Victor H. (1990), "Old Sinitic *<i>Myag</i>, Old Persian <i>Maguš</i> and English <i>Magician</i>", <i>Early China</i> <b>15</b>: 27–47</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Old+Sinitic+%2A%27%27Myag%27%27%2C+Old+Persian+%27%27Magu%C5%A1%27%27+and+English+%27%27Magician%27%27&amp;rft.jtitle=Early+China&amp;rft.aulast=Mair&amp;rft.aufirst=Victor+H.&amp;rft.au=Mair%2C+Victor+H.&amp;rft.date=1990&amp;rft.volume=15&amp;rft.pages=27%E2%80%9347&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Magi"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>.</li>
